      "span_text": "To test the calcium specificity of DB-BAPTA, we carried out a series of similar buffer injection experiments, except that DB-BAPTA solution was mixed with CaCl 2 in ratios of 20:1, 5:1, and 1:1, giving free Ca 2+ concentrations in the buffer of 0.08, 0.4, and 1.6 μM, respectively  ."
